<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4058.4.7>
    bibo:endPage "577" ;
    bibo:issue "4" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "561" ;
    bibo:volume "4058" ;
    dc:creator "Zhang, Feng; Deharveng, Louis" ;
    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "A revision of Pseudoparonella, Plumachaetas, Parachaetoceras and Lawrenceana (Collembola: Paronellidae), with description of three new species from New Caledonia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.236360>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.236361>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.236365> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.236360>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Habitus of Pseudoparonella seminigra sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/236360/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.236361>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2 – 9. Pseudoparonella seminigra sp. nov.: 2, Ant. III organ; 3, dorsal cephalic chaetotaxy; 4, dorsal body chaetotaxy from Th. II to Abd. IV (pseudopores not clearly seen on thorax); 5, trochanteral organ; 6, fore claw; 7, hind claw; 8, distal dorsum of manubrium; 9, mucro." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/236361/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.236365>
    dc:description "FIGURES 24 – 36. Plumachaetas yoshii sp. nov.: 24, body scales, tip rounded in the left and pointed in the right; 25, Ant. III organ; 26, Ant. IV apical chaetae; 27, labrum; 28, lateral process of labial palp; 29, maxillary outer lobe; 30, labial triangle chaetae, same as other two new species; 31, dorsal cephalic chaetotaxy; 32, dorsal body chaetotaxy from Th. II to Abd. IV (pseudopore not clearly seen on Abd. IV); 33, trochanteral organ; 34, mid claw; 35, hind claw; 36, mucro." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/236365/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

